" Use the build-in search function of firefox as long as `find()` is not
" working properly
" Unbinds <C-f> from scrolling, use <C-d> instead
unbind <C-f>
set tabsort mru
colorscheme dark
" ZZ Interfers with Firenvim, because there it is used to close Neovim and copy
" the buffer content into the form.
" If this is done while the Neovim frame is not focused, then Firefox is closed
" and the buffer content is lost.
unbind ZZ
" I'm not using `/` at all, so it is removed here and Github search behaves as
" normal
set leavegithubalone true
